code: // ------------------------- // Factory methods // ------------------------- static FallbackKey createFallbackKey(String key) {     return new FallbackKey(key, false). }
static FallbackKey createDeprecatedKey(String key) {     return new FallbackKey(key, true). }

// ------------------------------------------------------------------------ @Override public boolean equals(Object o) {     if (this == o) {         return true.     } else if (o != null && o.getClass() == FallbackKey.class) {         FallbackKey that = (FallbackKey) o.         return this.key.equals(that.key) && (this.isDeprecated == that.isDeprecated).     } else {         return false.     } }
@Override public String toString() {     return String.format("{key=%s, isDeprecated=%s}", key, isDeprecated). }
